          "user_thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV3ZsyPMrEbmnRJbxSupxbpG5ZfsK3pdnD-bBbakYI8iI5ZpieMkQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100",
          "description": "((2.75 stars))\n\na-okay Duane Reade location. it is one of the smaller locations with that older Duane Reade store aesthetic. packed with products -- and it surprisingly pretty organized given the size and amount of merch. normally stop here post-run to grab water and quick  snack bc it is convenient to one of my run routes. plus it is nearish to a large Trader Joe's. there is a huge section of snacks small-sized snacks (like trail mix etc.) than other locations. wish there was self-checkout at Duane Reade locations bc lines can build up here but staff tries to move customers as quick as possible.",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tWMVFrSlJhMVYzZEdGT2FsSjBhRWd0V0hWU2NrRRAB!2m1!1s0x0:0xf850a415c7c97547!3m1!1s2@1:CAIQACodChtycF9oOkV1QkJRa1V3dGFOalJ0aEgtWHVSckE%7C%7C?hl=en",
