          "description": "THE WORST STORE AND THE MOST INCOMPETENT PHARMACY DEPT. -\nI AM ON HOLD FOR 57 MINUTES!!!\nThe store manager is an absolute joke - aren't you embarrassed at least a little bit; I guess not.",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pkclVuVnFlRkZPTWxsNmNIZENNVm8zYVdOb2JsRRAB!2m1!1s0x0:0xf850a415c7c97547!3m1!1s2@1:CAIQACodChtycF9oOjdrUnVqeFFOMll6cHdCMVo3aWNoblE%7C%7C?hl=en",
          "date": "7 months ago",
          "date_iso8601": "2025-11-03T16:13:35+00:00"
        },
        {
          "username": "David Rivera",
          "rating": 1,
          "contributor_id": "112180584054090852281",
          "user_review_count": 2,
          "user_photo_count": 0,
          "user_thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocItHCcWdhDpA6gEUhJOi8MOgMaYSzWBJ8k-csiwtFXxhS5R9A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100",
          "description": "Yesterday July 26 around 9:20pm i was buying my items and then when i almost left  Duane reade the store clerk ran right behind me and took the umbrella out my backpack without saying nothing i told him what happened he accused me of stealing. had the umbrella for months and i told him to call the manager and he refused. He's in the wrong position \ud83d\udc4e",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT214RVdVRkNiekpOY2paTFNYWm9NRXRXTW5oUFZFRRAB!2m1!1s0x0:0xf850a415c7c97547!3m1!1s2@1:CAIQACodChtycF9oOmxEWUFCbzJNcjZLSXZoMEtWMnhPVEE%7C%7C?hl=en",
          "date": "10 months ago",
          "date_iso8601": "2025-07-27T19:21:50+00:00"
